# Dataset Documentation

## Data Source & Methodology

**Primary Source:** S&P Capital IQ  
**Period:** 2010-2023 (14 years)  
**Sector:** Technology  
**Geographic Focus:** Emerging Asian Markets  
**Sample Size:** [X firms / Y M&A transactions]

## Variable Dictionary

See `data_dictionary.xlsx` for complete variable definitions including:
- Financial metrics (ROA, ROE, gross profit)
- M&A indicators (deal value, post-M&A year dummy)
- Cultural variables (cultural distance proxy, country pairings)
- Control variables (firm size, leverage, market concentration)

## Data Limitations

- Data availability varies by country and firm size
- Some entries excluded due to missing values
- Cultural distance computed using Hofstede dimensions
- Emerging Asia definition per [World Bank/IMF classification]

## Confidentiality

Raw data not included (proprietary S&P Capital IQ licensing).  
Researchers can access via institutional license.

